        <h2>Project 2: Hospital Management System</h2>
        <img src="/get-logo-from-drive/hospitalManagementSystem.png" alt="Hospital Management System">

        <p>It is a web application designed to manage hospital operations efficiently. The system is responsive, providing a seamless experience for users across various devices.</p>
        <h3>Key Features:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Appointment Booking:</strong> Users can schedule appointments with doctors online, providing convenience and reducing waiting times.</li>
            <li><strong>Medicine Timing:</strong> Patients can access information about their prescribed medicine timings, ensuring proper medication adherence.</li>
            <li><strong>Visit History:</strong> A comprehensive record of past visits is available, allowing users to track their medical history.</li>
            <li><strong>Reports:</strong> Patients can view and download their medical reports through the system.</li>
            <li><strong>Role-Based Access:</strong> The system implements role-based access control with distinct roles for patients, doctors, nurses, and admins.</li>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Patients:</strong> Can view and manage their appointments, medicine schedules, visit history, and reports.</li>
                <li><strong>Doctors:</strong> Can access and manage appointment schedules, view patient records, and update medical information.</li>
                <li><strong>Nurses:</strong> Have access to patient records, medicine timings, and can update patient information as needed.</li>
                <li><strong>Admins:</strong> Have full access to system functionalities, including user management and system configuration.</li>
            </ul>
            <li><strong>Responsive Design:</strong> The system is designed to be accessible and user-friendly on various devices, including desktops, tablets, and smartphones.</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Technologies Used:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>HTML</li>
            <li>CSS</li>
            <li>JavaScript</li>
            <li>Backend technology (Node.js)</li>
            <li>Database (MongoDB)</li>
        </ul>
        <h3> Role:</h3>
        <p>As the developer, I'm responsible for the end-to-end development of this project, including designing the user interface, implementing functionality, and ensuring data security.</p>
        <h3>Challenges Faced:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Ensuring data confidentiality and security due to the sensitive nature of medical information.</li>
            <li>Implementing a user-friendly interface to accommodate users with varying levels of technical proficiency.</li>
            <li>Integrating appointment scheduling, medication tracking, and report generation seamlessly.</li>
            <li>Meeting regulatory requirements for handling medical data.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Outcome: The Hospital Management System enhances the efficiency of hospital operations, providing a user-friendly platform for patients to manage their medical appointments and records.</p>
